PLUM POX POTYVIRUS, SURVEILLANCE - CANADA (05)
**********************************************
A ProMED-mail post
<http://www.promedmail.org>
See Also
Plum pox potyvirus, surveillance - Canada 20000812.1339
Plum pox potyvirus, surveillance - Canada (02) 20000815.1357
